item.title: CVE-2022-34396|2024-08-03T09:07:16.135Z -- dell -- openmanage%20server%20administrator%20%28omsa%29
item.description: Dell OpenManage Server Administrator (OMSA) version 10.3.0.0 and earlier contains a DLL Injection Vulnerability. A local low privileged authenticated attacker could potentially exploit this vulnerability, leading to the execution of arbitrary executable on the operating system with elevated privileges. Exploitation may lead to a complete system compromise.
